Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----OP
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:23.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰かを悲しませてまで　笑えなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:27.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そう言って彼女は　うつむいてたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:34.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夜に泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:41.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冷たく張り付いて凍えている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:49.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}降り続く現実に傘などない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:55.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生きていく事が戦いなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:59.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そんな理由だけで閉じ込められた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:02.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}マイハートマイストーリー
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:09.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪のムコウが見えるの　輝いている
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:16.53,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ちいさな窓には　あの頃みたいに　青い空がうつる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:22.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ああ鳥のように飛べはしないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:34.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰かを悲しませたとき感じる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:42.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れないように　そっと目を閉じて　泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:23.73,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若能让你忘却伤痛 我宁愿舍弃笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:27.45,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如是言语的她 默然低下了头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:34.18,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}任凭泪水洗刷着夜色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:41.96,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冷漠蔓延着冻结一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:49.13,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仿佛这无可喘息的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:55.70,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生存就是战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:59.30,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}被这可悲的理由束缚着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:02.27,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My heart my story
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:09.84,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪水的彼岸 那闪耀的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:16.53,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}狭小的窗口中 满眼是往昔的蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:22.60,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}虽然无法像鸟儿一样飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:34.77,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为让悲伤永远铭记于心而生的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:42.06,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为了忘却而闭目哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----ED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:15.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}花は風に揺れ踊るように　雨は大地を潤すように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.69,0:21:20.06,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}この世界は寄り添い合い　生きてるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:31.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}なぜ人は傷付け合うの　なぜ別れは訪れるの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:37.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}君が遠くに行ってもまだ　いつもこの心の真ん中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:41.58,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}あの優しい笑顔で埋め尽くされたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:50.74,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}抱きしめた君の欠片に　痛み感じてもまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:54.52,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}繋がるから　信じてるよ　また逢えると
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:56.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I am waiting for your love
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:22:01.83,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you　I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.93,0:22:07.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}君の孤独を分けて欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.36,0:22:12.53,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you　I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.71,0:22:18.10,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}光でも闇でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:25.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}二人だから信じ合える
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:30.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}NO 離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:15.69,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}如同花朵随风起舞 如同雨水滋润大地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.69,0:21:20.06,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}这个世界如此紧密不分 如此活泼生机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:31.56,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}却为何人们要互相伤害 为何离别会突然降临
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:37.26,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}即便去往遥远的地方 你总是会活在我心底
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:41.58,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}那份温柔的笑颜依旧映在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:50.74,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}拥抱着你的碎片 刺痛着我的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:54.52,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}但心心相连 因为我坚信 会再见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:56.56,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I am waiting for your love
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:22:01.83,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you  I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.93,0:22:07.23,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}多么想分担你的孤寂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.36,0:22:12.53,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you  I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.71,0:22:18.10,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}无论身处黑暗或是光明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:25.19,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}只要在一起就可以相信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:30.61,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}永远不再分离
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.97,0:00:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚·肖汉博格制造Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.23,0:00:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 制造GN-DRIVER的理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.64,0:00:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.38,0:00:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武力介入只是为此的布局
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚的目的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.15,0:00:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引导人类的革新
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.05,0:00:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在变革之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.94,0:00:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.46,0:00:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你所领会到的极致吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者一定会再度…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.52,0:00:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时 请务必赐予我战斗的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.29,0:00:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.83,0:00:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所追求的是只有战斗者才能到达的极致
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.27,0:00:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年曾经对我说过 世界在扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.69,0:01:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 对他而言 存在价值只有不停的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.90,0:01:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.81,0:01:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是和你战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了那极致里的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你追求的只有胜利吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还有什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.62,0:01:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.12,0:01:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和未来相连的 明天!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀无赦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.02,0:01:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空手夺白刃!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.22,0:01:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的 战斗!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战…战斗吧 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.76,0:02:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劈了我 将胜利握于手中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不杀我!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.22,0:02:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要活着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.43,0:02:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着迎接明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了生存而战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈 露易丝·哈勒维的机体呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反应消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:02:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.00,0:02:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为 为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为纯种觉醒了么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是可以掌握人类命运的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你知道维塔的所在了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 王留美给的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到维塔了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗号解析完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐标是CZ9842R
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月球的背面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用超长焦望远镜观察该坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉格朗日2…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连殖民地开发都没有到过的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对藏东西而言 真是好地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在显示目标地点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这个区域的天体图叠在这个画面上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星的位置偏离了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光学迷彩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特 算出存在偏移的范围
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直径15公里!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.35,0:05:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有15公里!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大的物体被隐藏起来了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在月球的背面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:06:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐 收到实验室运输舰发来的暗号通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新装备到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独立治安维持部队A-LAWS 将以全部兵力进行天行者的歼灭作战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒作为反政府势力的最终堡垒的他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢取统一世界的真正和平
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待诸位的勇猛表现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,21艘巡洋舰和108架MS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以如此规模战力的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准将
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特许人士离开舰队了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随他们去吧 战场容不得他们随意行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里本斯发出的返回命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他终于最好觉悟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 还在计划之中哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为即将来临之物日益迫近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝…哈勒维…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人的仇? 我也有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为只有自己是不幸的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活该…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能过作为战力的东西都带过来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam各机的活力加强组件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有托勒密的补给
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连0-Gundam也带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上了粒子储藏容器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以能够进行一定时间的战斗哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 抓紧时间搬进去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在王留美指定的地点 舰队正在集结
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错了 维塔就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有变革者的根据地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破A-LAW的舰队 夺回维塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将是未曾有过的激战啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去 为了进行我自己的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库洛斯洛特君…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定了 不会再迷茫了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我也参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索玛·皮瑞斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有这样做的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算目的不同 我们都有前进理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 这种想法将于未来相连
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要为未来战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了解放变革者支配下的人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我和皮瑞斯这样的人 不会再度出现在世界上…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒联邦政府是我的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狙击变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要变革
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就无法迎接未来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补给结束后 托勒密将起航
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.69,0:09:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 现在托勒密缺少舵手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是就在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然能行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到月亮的另一面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜公主 有好多星星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢 非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都乖一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS正在拉格朗日2集结舰队?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从G1那里得到的情报哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者好像也打算到哪里去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从政变派那里也得到了同样的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还付了详细的战术计划…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布置完毕了 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于 审判降临了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由作为纯种而变革的刹那·F·塞艾 还是由我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.05,0:10:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来决定人类的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓武士道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了寻找死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了生存而战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓武士道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超望远光学摄像头 捕捉到敌方舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 一级战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.70,0:11:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳达小姐在实验室种出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要… 送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让玛丽娜小姐不高兴的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.72,0:11:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她不是那种关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:11:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去Gundam那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:11:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要死啊! 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密号 全甲板打开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要将维塔夺回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引导我吧… 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德先生 期待你的战果的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee 提艾利亚·爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索玛·皮瑞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫玛丽也行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想那么叫的话 就那么叫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.31,0:12:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Archer Arios
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷鲁亚·哈普狄斯姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索玛·皮瑞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向目标进发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim 出击准备完成的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:13:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽 看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim 洛克昂·斯特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.06,0:13:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹无虚发!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没问题么? 沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我 也想要找到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.35,0:13:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.47,0:13:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 刹那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.63,0:13:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0 Raiser 沙慈·库洛斯洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0 Raiser DOCKING-MODE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0 Raiser DOCKING-MODE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam从太空舰出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先遣部队 攻击开始!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别任务舰 给我好好干哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牵制敌方部队!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊～!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压缩粒子 完全解放!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺可以啊 这新装备!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事!? 敌舰竟然!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰 没有减速的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.31,0:15:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自杀攻击!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 用RAISER SWORD对付敌方舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RAISER系统 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM RAISER!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子干扰么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反相力场在广域内展开的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.49,0:15:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子射线的效果下降
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱么!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:16:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没在至近距离展开已经不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变更轨道 脱离这个力场!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想象中对应得还早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主力部队 攻击开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用数量压倒他们!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 粒子光束竟然!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导弹的残弹已经!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的数量多过头了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亚!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被突破了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷中弹!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,损伤情况…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 想一点点玩死我们么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌机 接近的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯… 什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩护天行者组织!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.37,0:18:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援军!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得真是时候!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON的武装…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预测到了反相力场?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.62,0:18:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将托勒密号冲向敌方舰队!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 竟然是KATARON?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.75,0:18:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就他们那点战力…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:19:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准将 我方的运输舰被!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运输舰又怎么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子光束来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劝告A-LAWS部队
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等揭竿而起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为联邦执行恶政的傀儡的A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无法称为军队
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界发展的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有通过全体人民的意见才可决定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.07,0:19:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等会对你们野蛮的行为定罪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而行正义与否将由市民决定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只可恶的女狐狸…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我打!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是反政府势力!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方部队接近过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS部队 攻击开始!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死身的克拉萨瓦～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:20:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此上阵～!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过对些运输舰你们在干什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们藏在僚舰的背后 无法攻击!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.27,0:20:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的友军不要理会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.33,0:20:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和敌人一起给我击落!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我方的士兵在!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别啰嗦 我说了打!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准将! 敌舰突破了反相力场!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G…Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Raiser
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱逐目标!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我想点办法啊～!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.13,0:22:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～好厉害!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.49,0:22:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这会儿克劳斯他们已经加入了战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.36,0:22:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争的… 光芒…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS舰队被突破了么…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.02,0:22:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类看来还真是喜欢战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.20,0:22:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你让他们这么做的么?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.03,0:23:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们引导到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.28,0:23:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应该也是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.84,0:23:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.86,0:23:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是比你们更上位种的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.27,0:23:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以说是创造神
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.10,0:23:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被野心支配的你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.14,0:23:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过脑量子波我可知道得一清二楚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.46,0:23:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾啊 里杰诺·瑞婕塔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.46,0:23:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里本斯·阿尔马克!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.09,0:23:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.92,0:23:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.29,0:23:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会引导人类的 是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.24,0:23:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里杰诺·瑞婕塔!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.19,0:24:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于现出身姿的变革者的大型母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.15,0:24:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在它面前的机师们有胜算么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.52,0:24:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.35,0:24:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命之华彩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.95,0:24:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡光芒闪过之处 便有生命陨落…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:10.87,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}残された夢のあと　踏みつける
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:15.99,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}気まぐれな死神が立ち止まった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:20.85,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}すれ違う僕を見る冷たく
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:25.75,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}愚かな罪をけしかけるように
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:31.03,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伸ばされた手をふりほどいた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.26,0:12:36.26,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}反逆のシナリオに舞い降りた堕天使
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.34,0:12:42.63,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}なぜ君は光の外にいるのか　気づいたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:50.39,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}もし僕じゃなく生まれたら　笑っていられたかな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:57.21,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無償の愛その中で　孤独など知らぬまま
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:13:07.34,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}郷愁を映し出す　遠い空を見つめた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:19.05,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どんなに願っても永久に触れられない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:26.13,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}負けていたんだ　自分の闇に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:33.32,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}奪われた儚き光　生きる証をつないで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:37.35,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どんな運命も受け入れて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:42.31,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕は生きる　最後の瞬間まで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:10.87,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}践踏着 残留的梦的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:15.99,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}随心所欲的死神伫立着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:20.85,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冷冷地注视擦身而过的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:25.75,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仿佛正在怂恿我犯下愚蠢的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:31.03,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}甩开他伸出的手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.26,0:12:36.26,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}叛逆的剧本里 飘落下堕落的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.34,0:12:42.63,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我已经知晓 为何你身处光芒之外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:50.39,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}倘若我不是作为我降临人世的话 是否就能一直笑逐颜开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:57.21,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}深陷毫无回报的爱中 孤独什么的我一概不知
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:13:07.34,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我一直凝望着 映照出乡愁的遥远的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:19.05,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无论再怎么许愿 那份永远还是遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:26.13,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我败给了 我自己的阴暗面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:33.32,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所掠夺的幻灭的光芒 维系着我生存过的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:37.35,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无论怎样的命运 我都会接受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:42.31,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我要生存下去 直到最后一刻


